step1-->click maven install to generate its jar file
step2---> start the docker
step3-->open cmd at the directory where the dockerfile of thet project is present
step4-->create the image for the project with the "name" as mentioned in the ".yaml: file
step5-->login into docker using cmd and push the image into it
step6-->open cmd at the directory where the .yaml file is present in the laptop and start the minikube
step7-->create the pod using ".yaml" file
step8-->give the port number for the pod to run 
step9-->open browser and generate the request that starts the project
step10-->stop the pod and delete the pod
step11-->stop the minikube
step12-->clear the image in the docker
step13--> stop the docker and exit from both cmds
